Clothespin with Built-in Charger: A clothespin with a built-in USB charger, allowing you to charge your device while using it to hang clothes.
Clothespin with LED Lights: A clothespin with built-in LED lights, allowing you to add some ambiance to your laundry room or clothesline.
Clothespin with-Hanging Clip: A clothespin with a built-in clip, allowing you to hang multiple items of clothing on one clothespin.
Clothespin with Memo Board: A clothespin with a built-in memo board, allowing you to write notes or reminders on it while hanging clothes.
